abstract: DealBook Online; British used car website Auto Trader Group says it is pricing its initial public offering at 2.35 pounds a share, or about $3.5 billion.
lead_paragraph: Funds advised by the European private-equity firm Apax Partners bought out its joint venture partner last year and renamed the company Auto Trader.

headline.main: Auto Trader Group Is Valued at $3.5 Billion in London I.P.O.
